                <p><g type="cross">+</g>
                    <expan><abbr>Χ</abbr><ex>ριστο</ex><abbr>ῦ</abbr></expan>
                        Χάριτι<lb/>ἐτελ<supplied reason="omitted">ε</supplied>ιώθη τὸ πᾶν<lb/>ἔργον
                    τῆς ψηφώσεως<lb/><expan><abbr>τ</abbr><ex>οῦ</ex></expan> Δαισίου τοῦ <num
                        value="615">ειχʹ</num><lb/>ἔτους
                            <expan><abbr>ἰνδ</abbr><ex>ικτιῶνο</ex><abbr>ς</abbr></expan>
                    <num value="5">εʹ</num> Κύριε<lb/>μνήσθητι Ἐγλῶνος<lb/>καὶ Μαξίμωνος<lb/>τῶν
                    δούλων<lb/>σοῦ.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>With Christ's Grace all the work of the mosaic was completed, (in the month of)
                    Daisios, in the year 615, indiction 5. Lord remember Eglon and Maximon your
                    servants.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
                <p>The date given in the era of Ascalon corresponds to June 512 CE.</p>
            </div>
